headline: FIS to Enhance Back-Office Operations for MUFG Securities Canada
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., May 28, 2025--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial technology, today announced it has been selected by MUFG Securities (Canada), Ltd. (MUSC) to power its back-office operations. As a broker dealer providing services to institutional clients in Canadian capital markets, MUSC chose FIS’ Post Trade Processing Platform to help streamline its back-office operations, mitigate risk, and ultimately help unlock business growth.
